                    <h2 class="section-heading">REFUGEES</h2>
                    <p>War and natural disasters have plagued the surfaces of multiple countries around the world. Thousands of families are forced from their homes and thousands more are forced across borders in an attempt to protect themselves and their children. They travel over miles of dangerous terrain for a chance at a safer life, sometimes even losing their lives in the process. Those who are lucky settle in safer countries, having come with little more than what they could carry on their backs. Many of these refugees choose to come to America, "the land of the free," to escape the violence they face at home. <br> <br> As the number of incoming refugees has increased, tension has risen. However, many groups have come forward to take action for the cause of the refugees. They are fighting to allow the refugees to continue their settlment in a safer land so they can create a better future for their families. </p>
